This paper deals with natural language processing and semantic parsing, which are core topics in the field of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also involves machine learning techniques for mapping natural language to Bash commands, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the creation of a new dataset, which could be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and software engineering (cs.SE) communities.
